
Pipeline for running bulk RNA-seq analysis.



To run a test example:
  sbatch ./run.sh example/params.yml

Update 5/24/22:
- cleaned up scripts
- moved working directory to c4 scratch

Update 12/16/21:
- Updated default version to no ribosomal quenching
- Default version uses CHR version of gencode hg38.p13 genome index



To change the memory, cpus on an individual step, go to it in the nextflow.nf and specify, e.g.
  memory '50 GB'
  cpus 12

To change the time: go to the nextflow.config
